Content.title: Lee Kelleher
Content.name: Lee Kelleher
Content.bodyText:
Fair play for persisting with the video diaries, the fear of being alone with a camera is enough to scare me off! haha

I wasn't aware of Microsoft Expression Encoder, (even though I signed up to the WebsiteSpark program), I'd put Expression down to a 'designer'-type app, with no further research.

I'll have to take a look, since I want to do some screencasts of my various Umbraco packages!

Keep up the good work.
